  "privacyPolicyTitle": "Privacy Policy",
  "privacySection1Title": "1. Data we collect",
  "privacySection1Body": "When you create an account we collect your name, email, and optional phone number. Your business card details and technical usage data are processed to provide the service.",
  "privacySection2Title": "2. How we use data",
  "privacySection2Body": "We use your data to manage your account, share your cards, maintain security, and improve the service. Marketing messages are sent only with your explicit consent.",
  "privacySection3Title": "3. Data sharing",
  "privacySection3Body": "We do not sell your personal data. Limited sharing may occur for legal obligations, service providers (hosting, analytics), or with your explicit consent.",
  "privacySection4Title": "4. Retention",
  "privacySection4Body": "We retain your data while your account is active. When you delete your account, data is deleted or anonymized within a reasonable period except where law requires retention.",
  "privacySection5Title": "5. Your rights",
  "privacySection5Body": "You may request access, correction, deletion, or restriction of processing. Contact us through the in-app Support section.",
  "privacySection6Title": "6. Security",
  "privacySection6Body": "We use encryption, access controls, and regular security reviews. No system is 100% secure; we recommend using a strong password.",
  "privacySection7Title": "7. Policy updates",
  "privacySection7Body": "We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be announced in the app. Continued use after an update means you accept the revised policy.",
  "termsOfUseTitle": "Terms of Use",
  "termsSection1Title": "1. Scope of service",
  "termsSection1Body": "Cardence provides digital business card creation, sharing, and management. By using the app you agree to these terms.",
  "termsSection2Title": "2. Account creation",
  "termsSection2Body": "You are responsible for providing accurate, up-to-date registration information. Do not share your password with others.",
  "termsSection3Title": "3. Acceptable use",
  "termsSection3Body": "You may not use the service unlawfully, deceptively, or in ways that infringe others' rights. You are solely responsible for your card content.",
  "termsSection4Title": "4. Intellectual property",
  "termsSection4Body": "The Cardence brand, interface, and software belong to Cardence. You own your card content and grant us a limited license to operate the service.",
  "termsSection5Title": "5. Service changes",
  "termsSection5Body": "We may change the service to improve features or meet legal obligations. Material updates may be communicated in-app or by email.",
  "termsSection6Title": "6. Limitation of liability",
  "termsSection6Body": "The service is provided \"as is\". We exercise reasonable care but do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free operation. To the extent permitted by law we are not liable for indirect damages.",
  "termsSection7Title": "7. Contact",
  "termsSection7Body": "For questions about these terms, contact us through the in-app Support section.",
